---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const playStoreUrl = 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=it.sherlock.polizze';
---
<footer class="bg-navy-900 border-t border-navy-800 mt-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
    <div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-400 to-gold-600 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-4 h-4 text-navy-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7" />
            <line x1="16" y1="16" x2="21" y2="21" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="notranslate font-extrabold text-white" translate="no">Sherlock</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">
        Il detective delle tue polizze assicurative. Capisci cosa firmi,
        contesta ciò che non torna.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-navy-500 mt-4">
        Sherlock è uno strumento di analisi AI. <strong class="text-navy-300">Non sostituisce un avvocato o un consulente assicurativo</strong>:
        è un'assistenza informativa per orientarti e generare bozze di reclamo da
        rivedere prima dell'invio.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-navy-500 mb-3">Sito</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-navy-300">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/abbonati" class="hover:text-white">Abbonamento</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guide" class="hover:text-white">Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="/arbitro-assicurativo" class="hover:text-white">Ricorso all'Arbitro Assicurativo</a></li>
        <li><a href="/reclamo-ivass" class="hover:text-white">Reclamo &amp; IVASS</a></li>
        <li><a href="/sinistro-respinto" class="hover:text-white">Sinistro respinto</a></li>
        <li><a href="/esempio-report" class="hover:text-white">Esempio report</a></li>
        <li><a href="/esempio-lettera" class="hover:text-white">Esempio lettera</a></li>
        <li><a href="/trasparenza" class="hover:text-white">Trasparenza dati</a></li>
        <li><a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white">Privacy</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-navy-500 mb-3">Prova Sherlock</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-navy-300 mb-4">
        <li>
          <a href="/app/" class="hover:text-white">
            Apri dal browser (Web/iPhone) →
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row md:flex-col gap-3">
        <a
          href={playStoreUrl}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-black hover:bg-navy-800 border border-navy-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 transition-colors"
          aria-label="Scarica Sherlock su Google Play"
        >
          <svg viewBox="0 0 512 512" class="w-8 h-8 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
            <path fill="#EA4335" d="M89 483.9c-9.6-4.6-16.6-13.4-19.1-24.1L285 256 69.9 52.2c2.5-10.7 9.5-19.5 19.1-24.1L338 256z"/>
            <path fill="#FBBC04" d="M338 256l70.5-70.5c15.1 8.4 15.1 30.6 0 39l-70.5 40Z"/>
            <path fill="#4285F4" d="M285 256 69.9 52.2C74.5 50 79.7 48.8 85 48.8c5.7 0 11.6 1.4 17 4.4l236 133.3z"/>
            <path fill="#34A853" d="M338 325.5 102 458.8c-5.4 3-11.3 4.4-17 4.4-5.3 0-10.5-1.2-15.1-3.4L285 256z"/>
          </svg>
          <div class="text-left leading-tight">
            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy-300">Scarica su</div>
            <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Google Play</div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/ios"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-black hover:bg-navy-800 border border-navy-700 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 transition-colors"
          aria-label="Istruzioni per installare Sherlock su iPhone"
        >
          <svg viewBox="0 0 384 512" class="w-7 h-8 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
            <path fill="#ffffff" d="M318.7 268.7c-.2-36.7 16.4-64.4 50-84.8-18.8-26.9-47.2-41.7-84.7-44.6-35.5-2.8-74.3 20.7-88.5 20.7-15 0-49.4-19.7-76.4-19.7C63.3 141.2 4 184.8 4 273.5q0 39.3 14.4 81.2c12.8 36.7 59 126.7 107.2 125.2 25.2-.6 43-17.9 75.8-17.9 31.8 0 48.3 17.9 76.4 17.9 48.6-.7 90.4-82.5 102.6-119.3-65.2-30.7-61.7-90-61.7-91.9zm-56.6-164.2c27.3-32.4 24.8-61.9 24-72.5-24.1 1.4-52 16.4-67.9 34.9-17.5 19.8-27.8 44.3-25.6 71.9 26.1 2 49.9-11.4 69.5-34.3z"/>
          </svg>
          <div class="text-left leading-tight">
            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy-300">Installa su</div>
            <div class="text-base font-semibold text-white">iPhone</div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="text-navy-500 text-xs pt-3">it.sherlock.polizze</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-navy-800 px-5 py-5 max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-3 text-xs text-navy-500">
    <div class="notranslate" translate="no">© {year} Sherlock — ScapLAB</div>
    <div>Sviluppato in Italia 🇮🇹</div>
  </div>
</footer>
